## 第4次测量


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
cur_dat <- avg_perf |>
  filter(time == 4) |>
  select(-c(time, SID)) |>
  as.matrix()
mgm_obj <- mgm::mgm(
  cur_dat,
  type = rep("g", ncol(cur_dat)),
  level = rep(1, ncol(cur_dat)),
  ruleReg = "OR",
  pbar = FALSE
)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
Note that the sign of parameter estimates is stored separately; see ?mgm
```


