## 第8次测量


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
cur_dat <- avg_perf |>
  filter(time == 8) |>
  select(-c(time, SID)) |>
  as.matrix()
mgm_obj <- mgm::mgm(
  cur_dat,
  type = rep("g", ncol(cur_dat)),
  level = rep(1, ncol(cur_dat)),
  ruleReg = "OR",
  pbar = FALSE
)
```

